      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 it is offered strictly as-is, and buyers should have clear, realistic expectations before inquiring. The exterior shows significant wear, including deep scratches, scuffs, dents, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily soiled upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general neglect throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect to invest in repairs before relying on this vehicle for regular use. It is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the risks involved. No warranties or guarantees are provided, and all sales are final. Please inspect thoroughly before purchasing.",
