      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you before you consider purchasing. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 the paint is faded and dull in multiple areas, with visible scratches, chips, and at least one area of surface rust that will require attention. Body panels may show minor dents or dings consistent with years of use. The interior is worn throughout, with noticeable damage to upholstery, trim pieces, and surfaces. Mechanically, the vehicle runs but has known issues that will require repair \u2014 expect to invest in maintenance or fixes before relying on it for regular daily driving. This car is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is prepared for the realities of its current state. We believe in full transparency: this is not a turn-key vehicle, and the price reflects that honestly.",
